{"tid":113764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"侏儒都呃到蝦條連登仔仲有咩好講？","createTime":"2017-02-09T08:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T19:17:45.000Z","uid":78660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"def7242b894a7abc567671121c0b02b5ba8d33d0","tid":113764,"uid":78660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:50:51.000Z","msg":"在過去的1月，Macy跟丈夫鄭啟文（Kevin）剛慶祝結婚三周年，回想過去三年的婚姻生活，Macy只能用開心、甜蜜來形容。2013年對於Macy來說是人生的轉捩點，當時正就讀香港教育大學幼兒教育Year 1的她，經朋友介紹下在一次影展上認識當攝影師、比她大9年的Kevin。「當初真的沒有想過會和他一起，接觸Kevin時很欣賞他，雖然身體上有殘障，但卻沒有放棄，更有很多搞作，甚至會搞攝影展，覺得他很有才華所以對他有很深刻的印象。」後來二人再有單獨約會的機會，Kevin更對她表白，最終發展成情侶。<br />\n<br />\n問到她當初有否因Kevin身體缺陷而想過拒絕對方，Macy說：「除了外表之外，其實他跟一般人沒有分別，雖然他坐輪椅，但他是一個很活躍的人，又喜歡到處去影相，所以去過的地方也比我多，連拍拖都會帶我去郊外，會到上水古洞、稻田等，一直只會行街shopping的我，也從未想像過香港有這樣美的景色。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19歲停學結婚生女<br />\n<br />\n在拍拖初期Macy說身邊的朋友甚至父母也未有太大的反應，「只是有時街上的途人會有奇異的目光看我們，有的會估我們是什麼關係，但總之他們沒有話我們，我們也不會理會。」至於家人方面，在她發現懷孕，並決定跟Kevin結婚，父母就有意見。「他們不是反對我們結婚，只是勸我要想清楚，始終我只有19歲，所以要我考慮清楚，建議我再拍多幾年拖，相處時間長一些才決定，但仍會尊重我的決定。」Macy當時已認定Kevin就是她的結婚對象，也想跟這個人一起走下去，毅然決定停學，與Kevin結婚。<br />\n<br />\n邊個話要高大靚仔<br />\n屌你個矮仔連波皮都掂唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfebef09c8a3e64c40388bcd502741b5fabc61b7","tid":113764,"uid":28013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"原來咁樣就係呃蝦條<br />\n學到野"},{"pid":"7e8f90d02c5148a56b0b49f323467f609a17f205","tid":113764,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"..<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知咩叫呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n擺明係呃家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f9ee6175c8312b3fc6c7bc79344cbbd5897321","tid":113764,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"過幾年實後悔"},{"pid":"82ee3f6e361851e4726ce2bb4580441e1ba687f2","tid":113764,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"真愛"},{"pid":"3011c3e4779681aff5b5ad9a2a764c91f0d918b3","tid":113764,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"我有太古城既話， 拎張屋契印上件print tee度， 行出街 大把女食  走去元天屯公屋行一轉包保精盡人亡"},{"pid":"231a4e54568db62734dfdcc7fd43698e87845351","tid":113764,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20131227/52031123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20131227%2F52031123&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=824d1799\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20131227%2F52031123&h=57af018f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20131227/52031123</a><br />\n住太古城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013f65aa26dc4d19893b993b394f28d312b991b9","tid":113764,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f185a1024bbb18f35ffeea2fe55120b4686b7e01","tid":113764,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"人地住太古城"},{"pid":"6aa05dfa62a12bc4ccf653a59d7b236ab2d60bcd","tid":113764,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地住太古城</blockquote><br />\n真愛"},{"pid":"3e187b16a03925b9eb2a8416943f0e24663b7daa","tid":113764,"uid":78660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地住太古城</blockquote><br />\n真愛</blockquote><br 